question: Within a radius of 70 kilometers, where can I find  a restaurant from Steinhart Aquarium, CA towards Veterans Plaza, Milpitas, CA?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.465976 37.769485)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-121.898718 37.433082)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.465976 37.769485)',4326)::geography, 70000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.465976 37.769485)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
